# MediaTools Documentation Index

Recommended reading order:

1. [Root README](../README.md.en): Purpose, installation, launching, and commands
2. [WORKFLOW.md.en](../WORKFLOW.md.en): Currently recommended workflows
3. [ARCHITECTURE.md.en](../ARCHITECTURE.md.en): Current code structure and maintenance boundaries
4. This document: Specialized document index and document status

